I recommend buying an Arduino kit, like this one:
https://www.amazon.ca/Smraza-Tutorials-Compatible-MEGA2560-Components/dp/B06XXYVWVJ
That way, you won’t need to purchase the Aruino Pin Components, Arduino UNO with Programming Cable, resistors, and 9g Micro Servo separately. 

Regardless, here’s the part list needed:

Shrink Tubing:
https://www.amazon.ca/Zacro-Shrink-Tubes-Tubing-Assortment/dp/B07B2XJW95

5mm LED lights:
https://www.amazon.ca/uxcell®-100Pcs-Ultra-Bright-Emitting-12000MCD/dp/B00W8YY0YS

Arduino Pin Components:
https://www.amazon.ca/Gikfun-Breakable-Header-2-54mm-Arduino/dp/B01LYYUSOH

Arduino UNO with Programing Cable:
https://www.amazon.ca/kuman-Board-ATmega328P-Cable-Arduino/dp/B016D5KOOC

Rocker Switch:
https://www.amazon.ca/XT-AUTO-Rocker-Toggle-Control/dp/B01KRL8MBA

Push Button:
https://www.amazon.ca/SODIAL-Momentary-Round-Button-Switch/dp/B00F4MGQU2

9g Micro Servo:
https://www.amazon.ca/RioRand%C2%AE-Micro-Servo-Airplane-Genuine/dp/B00M8RGGFG

Female USB Cable:
https://www.amazon.ca/UGREEN-Adapter-Samsung-Controller-Smartphone/dp/B00LN3LQKQ

Long Male USB Cable:
https://www.amazon.ca/Vinpie-Premium-Braided-Charging-Motorola/dp/B071NRG89M

Small Zip Ties:
https://www.amazon.com/South-Main-Hardware-848100-100-Pack/dp/B01977VBBS

5x7 Acrylic Frame (example):
https://www.amazon.ca/MCS-Acrylic-Picture-7-Inch-Vertical/dp/B0000A9ZBQ

80% Window Tint:
https://www.amazon.ca/VViViD-Headlight-Taillight-Air-Release-1-49ft/dp/B01GQRQ996
